7. Gamification Master Class with Gabe Zichermann: This excellent and informative video course runs 3 hours and 7 minutes, and can be purchased from O'Reilly Media at http://shop.oreilly.com/product/0636920017622.do. Frequently, you can find codes on O'Reilly's website that allow you to purchase the video for 50% off the list price.
