13. Adrien Treuille: Next-Generation Citizen Science http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ia2qBqfZROE
14. [Saatchi S Perspective: Gabe Zichermann](http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-I-cZrbWz-I&feature=colike) Where has intrinsic motivation gotten us so far? Gabe Zichermann talks about the use of game thinking and game mechanics to engage people and solve problems. Saatchi S asks Gabe about the world of possibilities for positive societal change with gamification.
15. [Amy Jo Kim:  Smart Gamification](http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=F4YP-hGZTuA) A talk by Professor Werbach's guest speaker on building sustainability in gamification
